{"tid":1686023,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[文具] 有冇人知咩係玻璃線","createTime":"2019-11-01T01:31:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-04T16:01:02.000Z","uid":118219,"like":17,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"b0179a7a6e16d888f82fac4bd4c7c39e993919ed","tid":1686023,"uid":118219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T01:31:21.000Z","msg":"老豆話最近秋風起想一齊去放風箏<br />\n叫我買線個陣小心唔好買咗玻璃紙 好易界死人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但我又搵唔到太多關於玻璃線嘅資料 有冇巴打知係乜黎<br />\n等我小心啲唔好買錯嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢啲咁高危險嘅文具大家記得唔好亂用<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"770d2721401e45169d51a499f89794acc2693339","tid":1686023,"uid":118219,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T01:31:52.000Z","msg":"係唔好買玻璃線"},{"pid":"dd50029d20cca2c157cb6b1905bb060c535eff07","tid":1686023,"uid":118219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T01:32:53.000Z","msg":"好似開錯台添"},{"pid":"543ccd108eba6c52943bd17d3d6f5ef81419402f","tid":1686023,"uid":118219,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T01:33:23.000Z","msg":"有冇人知啊 想今個weekend去放風箏"},{"pid":"be51aa5b74c123162bb6e44c2fbd68c29eff5a30","tid":1686023,"uid":118219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T01:37:08.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"a13f719227b210f9975563ac3c64e16058e72ffa","tid":1686023,"uid":118219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T01:38:52.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"5a6e6dffe5779555eacaa8b9fc474fb1f0214ca8","tid":1686023,"uid":118219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T01:46:29.000Z","msg":"再推"},{"pid":"bfe5d1504fa6c35f42f08c3cdd01193475a945e4","tid":1686023,"uid":53604,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T01:52:18.000Z","msg":"印象中死過人, 千祈唔好亂玩"},{"pid":"337e12bc5528005544e4d3dad05f882df02c47b5","tid":1686023,"uid":53604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T01:52:53.000Z","msg":"風箏線看似又軟又幼，但其實亦有驚人殺傷力，一般的風箏線以棉線、尼龍及魚絲混合而成，質地較軟，用手直接觸摸也不會弄損，但部分非主流人士喜歡「𠍇鳶」，以𠍇斷別人風箏為樂，他們除講求技巧外，所採用的風箏線亦與眾不同。<br />\n<br />\n難於察覺 防不勝防<br />\n<br />\n    多年前曾興起自製玻璃線，先把玻璃磨碎，然後混入白膠漿中，再塗於風箏線上，殺傷力十分巨大，但現時已甚少人沿用此法。「𠍇鳶」人士現時所採用的玻璃線，大多產自印尼，質地較硬，一卷約售五十元，雖然不是真的以玻璃製造，但有人會於線上塗上膠水，使風箏線產生凹凸不平效果，令𠍇鳶時得心應手，危險性亦相對增加。<br />\n    不過，即使是普通風箏線，當電單車以高速駛過時，亦足以令司機皮破肉開，加上風箏線多以白線為主，根本難憑肉眼察覺，令人防不勝防。除釀成交通意外，風箏線𠍇傷途人的事件亦時有發生。今年四月底，一名女途人在屯門掃管笏被風箏線𠍇傷頸部，幸傷勢並無大礙，但已足見風箏線可傷人於無形，不可不慎。"},{"pid":"1291138853f1f35e22d7f3d032ff4554507b9a7e","tid":1686023,"uid":53604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T01:54:42.000Z","msg":"玩風箏咪玩風箏囉<br />\n做乜要整斷人地d風箏 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 此風不可長<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f137201ea61c1b136460c2383f3bcb132ee6f4c6","tid":1686023,"uid":118219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T11:02:18.000Z","msg":"咁恐怖嫁咩"},{"pid":"ecc102bc12ac4b868cd7c2b68d0d75a521497954","tid":1686023,"uid":128594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T11:02:51.000Z","msg":"細細聽到都覺得好恐怖<br />\n<br />\n支持&ldquo;甴近平&rdquo;, 由你我做起(2)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1686740\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1686740</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n甴近平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"baccbb84803c8df2f68e1774bd661192946f9de6","tid":1686023,"uid":48887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T11:04:29.000Z","msg":"鬼船？"},{"pid":"b5c13f0957020d4046f08f327eea3271f54eed75","tid":1686023,"uid":195601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T11:05:12.000Z","msg":"唔該唔好再講呢啲"},{"pid":"69cb1af427d76bbdb9e7a1d85f5ac72f0bb69e52","tid":1686023,"uid":51717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cite